"Unknown license state." = "许可证状态未知。";

/* --- Create-vault form --- */
"New vault path (…/my.vault)" = "新保险库路径（…/my.vault）";
"Capacity" = "容量";
"size" = "大小";
"MB" = "MB";
"Choose any size you want (e.g. 64, 512, 4096…). The vault file is always exactly this size on disk, no matter how much you store — that's part of the deniability." = "选择任意你想要的大小（例如 64、512、4096…）。无论你存储多少，保险库文件在磁盘上始终正好占用此大小——这是可否认性的一部分。";
"Generated (recommended)" = "生成的（推荐）";
"My own" = "我自己的";
"There is no recovery, and there is no self-destruct: the file looks like random data and your passphrase is the ONLY thing protecting it. That is why it must be strong — and why you must not lose it." = "没有恢复，也没有自毁：文件看起来像随机数据，而你的密码短语是唯一保护它的东西。因此它必须足够强——也因此你绝不能丢失它。";
"Also require a YubiKey (hardware key)" = "同时要求 YubiKey（硬件密钥）";
"YubiKey PIN (leave blank if none)" = "YubiKey PIN 码（若无则留空）";
"Also enrol a backup key now" = "现在同时注册一个备份密钥";
"You'll enrol the keys one at a time: insert the first key and touch it, then swap to the second when asked. Either key will open the vault — keep the backup somewhere safe and separate." = "你将逐个注册密钥：插入第一个密钥并轻触，然后在提示时换上第二个。任一密钥都能打开保险库——请将备份密钥保存在安全且独立的地方。";
"You'll be asked to TOUCH the key to enrol it. Then a copy of this vault can't be brute-forced without the physical key. Lose your only key and the vault is gone — there is no recovery, so a backup key is recommended." = "系统会要求你轻触密钥以完成注册。之后，没有实体密钥就无法暴力破解此保险库的副本。若丢失唯一的密钥，保险库将无法找回——没有恢复，因此建议设置备份密钥。";
"Record my identity in this vault" = "在此保险库中记录我的身份";
"Stores “%@” inside the encrypted vault — visible only after unlock. ⚠︎ This ATTRIBUTES the vault to you if it is ever decrypted. Leave OFF if you need deniability." = "将「%@」存储在加密保险库内——仅在解锁后可见。⚠︎ 一旦保险库被解密，这会将其归属于你。如果你需要可否认性，请保持关闭。";
"Activate a license first to record your identity." = "请先激活许可证以记录你的身份。";
"Create and open" = "创建并打开";
"Creating a vault needs an active license. Activate one with “Manage license…” below. (Opening existing vaults always works.)" = "创建保险库需要有效的许可证。请通过下方的「管理许可证…」激活一个。（打开现有保险库始终可用。）";
"Choose where to save the vault (Choose…)." = "选择保险库的保存位置（「选择…」）。";
"Generate a passphrase." = "生成一个密码短语。";
"Tick the box confirming you saved the passphrase." = "勾选复选框以确认你已保存密码短语。";
"Enter a passphrase." = "输入一个密码短语。";
"Passphrases don't match." = "两个密码短语不一致。";
"Passphrase must reach “Very strong” (4/4)." = "密码短语必须达到「非常强」（4/4）。";
"Regenerate" = "重新生成";
"≈ 129 bits — 10 random words" = "≈ 129 位 — 10 个随机单词";
"I have written this passphrase down somewhere safe" = "我已将此密码短语记在安全的地方";
"Confirm passphrase" = "确认密码短语";
"Must reach “Very strong” (4/4). Tip: 5+ random, unrelated words beat any short clever password." = "必须达到「非常强」（4/4）。提示：5 个以上互不相关的随机单词胜过任何简短而巧妙的密码。";
"Choose Folder" = "选择文件夹";
"Choose the folder for the new vault. You'll set its name back in the Farewell window. An existing vault is never overwritten." = "为新保险库选择文件夹。你将在 Farewell 窗口中设置其名称。现有保险库绝不会被覆盖。";

