"Couldn't open it. Check the passphrase — and, if this vault uses a YubiKey, that it's plugged in and you entered its PIN." = "无法打开。请检查密码短语——如果此保险库使用 YubiKey，请检查它已插入且你已输入其 PIN 码。";
"Vault header has been tampered with" = "保险库标头已被篡改";
"Counter rollback detected" = "检测到计数器回滚";
"Passphrase too weak — use a stronger or generated one" = "密码短语太弱——请使用更强的或生成的密码短语";
"No YubiKey detected — plug it in and try again." = "未检测到 YubiKey——请插入后重试。";
"YubiKey check failed — wrong PIN, or it wasn't touched in time." = "YubiKey 检查失败——PIN 码错误，或未及时轻触。";
"More than one key is plugged in. With a PIN, please leave only the key you're unlocking with plugged in (trying a PIN on the wrong key can lock it), then try again." = "插入了多个密钥。使用 PIN 码时，请仅保留你要用来解锁的那个密钥（在错误的密钥上尝试 PIN 码可能将其锁定），然后重试。";
"Not a Farewell vault file" = "不是 Farewell 保险库文件";
"Vault uses a format this build cannot read" = "保险库使用了此版本无法读取的格式";

