"Keys" = "密钥";
"Hardware-key management." = "硬件密钥管理。";
"Vault passphrase" = "保险库密码短语";
"Current key's PIN (leave blank if no PIN or no key)" = "当前密钥的 PIN 码（若无 PIN 码或无密钥则留空）";
"Cancel" = "取消";
"Show keys" = "显示密钥";
"Reading keys…" = "正在读取密钥…";
"Done" = "完成";
"Passphrase-only — no hardware key enrolled." = "仅密码短语——未注册任何硬件密钥。";
"Only one key opens this vault. **Lose it and the vault is gone forever — there is no recovery.** Enrol a backup key below so either key works." = "只有一个密钥能打开此保险库。**丢失它，保险库将永远丢失——没有恢复。** 请在下方注册一个备份密钥，使两个密钥都可用。";
"Key %lld" = "密钥 %lld";
"Remove (last)" = "移除（最后一个）";
"Revoke" = "吊销";
"Revoke this key?" = "吊销此密钥？";
"It will no longer open this vault; the other keys still will. Revoking uses only your passphrase, then you'll touch a remaining key once to reopen the vault." = "它将不再打开此保险库；其他密钥仍可使用。吊销仅使用你的密码短语，然后你将轻触一个剩余密钥一次以重新打开保险库。";
"Remove your last key?" = "移除你的最后一个密钥？";
"Remove last key" = "移除最后一个密钥";
"This turns the vault back into passphrase-only: the passphrase alone will open it, and opening becomes slower again (by design). Insert the key now — you'll touch it once so it can be safely removed." = "这会将保险库恢复为仅密码短语模式：仅凭密码短语即可打开，而打开会再次变慢（出于设计）。现在请插入密钥——你将轻触它一次，以便安全地移除它。";
"Add a hardware key" = "添加硬件密钥";
"Add a backup key" = "添加备份密钥";
"Require a physical key (plus your passphrase) to open this vault. Insert the new key and touch it twice to enrol." = "要求实体密钥（外加你的密码短语）来打开此保险库。插入新密钥并轻触两次以完成注册。";
"Enrol another key so any enrolled key opens this vault. Insert your current key and touch it, then swap to the new key and touch it twice. Keep the backup safe and separate — there's no recovery if you lose every key." = "注册另一个密钥，使任一已注册密钥都能打开此保险库。插入你当前的密钥并轻触，然后换上新密钥并轻触两次。请将备份密钥保存在安全且独立的地方——若丢失所有密钥则没有恢复。";
"Set/enter this key's PIN (leave blank if none)" = "设置/输入此密钥的 PIN 码（若无则留空）";
"New key's PIN (leave blank if none)" = "新密钥的 PIN 码（若无则留空）";
"Name (optional)" = "名称（可选）";
"Add key…" = "添加密钥…";
"Add backup…" = "添加备份…";
"This vault already has the maximum of %lld keys." = "此保险库已达到最多 %lld 个密钥。";
"Working…" = "正在处理…";
"Follow the prompts on your key — insert, swap, and touch as asked. Don't unplug a key unless you're told to." = "按照密钥上的提示操作——按要求插入、更换和轻触。除非有提示，否则请勿拔下任何密钥。";

