/* --- Import bar --- */
"New note" = "新建笔记";
"Create a new empty note and open it in the editor. It lives only inside the encrypted vault." = "创建一个新的空白笔记并在编辑器中打开。它仅存在于加密保险库内。";
"1 pass" = "1 遍";
"3 passes" = "3 遍";
"7 passes" = "7 遍";
"Overwrite passes. 1 is enough on any modern drive; 3/7 exist only for standards that mandate them and add nothing on an SSD." = "覆写遍数。在任何现代驱动器上 1 遍即足够；3/7 仅为强制要求的标准而存在，在 SSD 上没有任何额外作用。";
"Shred originals" = "粉碎原件";
"After importing, securely overwrite and delete the source file. On a hard disk this physically erases it; on an SSD wear-leveling means it's best-effort only (no guarantee) — the real protection is the encrypted vault." = "导入后，安全地覆写并删除源文件。在硬盘上这会将其物理擦除；在 SSD 上，磨损均衡意味着这只是尽力而为（不保证）——真正的保护是加密保险库。";
"Drag files here, or click Import. Files are encrypted into the vault; nothing is written elsewhere." = "将文件拖到此处，或点击「导入」。文件将被加密到保险库；不会在其他任何地方写入内容。";
"Imported %lld; last error: %@" = "已导入 %lld 个；最后一个错误：%@";
"Imported 1 file." = "已导入 1 个文件。";
"Imported %lld files." = "已导入 %lld 个文件。";
"Original securely erased (overwritten %lld× in place on a hard disk)." = "原件已安全擦除（在硬盘上原地覆写 %lld 次）。";
"Original overwritten + deleted — but this is an SSD: wear-leveling means the cells may persist. The real protection is the encrypted vault, not the wipe." = "原件已覆写并删除——但这是 SSD：磨损均衡意味着单元可能仍然残留。真正的保护是加密保险库，而非擦除。";
"Original overwritten + deleted (storage type unknown; treated as flash — no physical-erase guarantee)." = "原件已覆写并删除（存储类型未知；按闪存处理——不保证物理擦除）。";

/* --- File viewer --- */
"Save" = "保存";
"Save the changes back into the encrypted vault. Nothing is written to disk." = "将更改保存回加密保险库。不会向磁盘写入任何内容。";
"Edit" = "编辑";
"Edit this text file in the app and save it back into the vault. Nothing is written to disk." = "在应用内编辑此文本文件并保存回保险库。不会向磁盘写入任何内容。";
"Export…" = "导出…";
"Write a decrypted copy of this file to disk, outside the vault. Shows a warning first." = "将此文件的解密副本写入磁盘，保险库之外。会先显示警告。";
"The vault isn’t open." = "保险库未打开。";

/* --- Export warning --- */
"Export a decrypted copy?" = "导出解密副本？";
"You are about to write the decrypted contents of “%@” to a regular file on disk. Once written, that file leaves Farewell's protection:" = "你即将把「%@」的解密内容写入磁盘上的普通文件。一旦写入，该文件就离开了 Farewell 的保护：";
"Spotlight will index its contents" = "聚焦（Spotlight）会索引其内容";
"QuickLook will cache a thumbnail" = "快速查看（QuickLook）会缓存缩略图";
"Time Machine will back it up (if enabled)" = "时间机器（Time Machine）会备份它（若已启用）";
"Apps that open it keep it in Recent Items" = "打开它的应用会将其保留在「最近使用的项目」中";
"Farewell can no longer track or recall it" = "Farewell 将无法再跟踪或召回它";
"Use the in-app viewer instead unless you genuinely need an external copy. For device-to-device transfer, Farewell-to-Farewell P2P (coming later) never writes cleartext to disk." = "除非你确实需要外部副本，否则请改用应用内查看器。对于设备间传输，Farewell 到 Farewell 的点对点功能（即将推出）绝不会向磁盘写入明文。";
"Export anyway" = "仍然导出";
"This file will be written UNENCRYPTED outside the vault." = "此文件将以未加密形式写入保险库之外。";

/* --- Migrate sheet --- */
"Migrate / rotate vault" = "迁移 / 轮换保险库";
"Re-encrypts everything into a brand-new vault file with fresh keys (the same passphrase). Your files are copied and verified before anything is replaced; nothing is written to disk in the clear. The original is kept until you delete it." = "将所有内容重新加密到一个全新的保险库文件中，使用新密钥（相同的密码短语）。在替换任何内容之前，你的文件会被复制并验证；不会以明文向磁盘写入任何内容。在你删除之前会保留原文件。";
"New size" = "新大小";
"Keep current capacity" = "保持当前容量";
"Shrink to fit contents" = "收缩以适应内容";
"Destination:" = "目标位置：";
"Needs about %@; %@ free here." = "大约需要 %@；此处可用 %@。";
"This vault requires a YubiKey" = "此保险库需要 YubiKey";
"Migrate" = "迁移";
"Use Folder" = "使用此文件夹";
"Not enough space on %@: the new vault needs about %@ but only %@ is free. Choose “Shrink to fit” or a different drive." = "%@ 上空间不足：新保险库大约需要 %@，但仅有 %@ 可用。请选择「收缩以适应内容」或其他驱动器。";
"A file named “%@” already exists in that folder. Pick another destination." = "该文件夹中已存在名为「%@」的文件。请选择其他目标位置。";
"Migration failed: %@. Your original vault is unchanged." = "迁移失败：%@。你的原始保险库未更改。";
"Migrated. The previous vault is kept as “%@” — delete it once you’ve confirmed this one works." = "已迁移。先前的保险库保留为「%@」——确认此保险库可用后请将其删除。";
"Migrated to %@. Your original vault is unchanged — delete it when ready." = "已迁移到 %@。你的原始保险库未更改——准备好后请将其删除。";
"Migration verified but the file swap failed: %@. Your original vault is unchanged." = "迁移已验证，但文件交换失败：%@。你的原始保险库未更改。";

/* --- Create-vault rename notice --- */
"“%@” already existed — created “%@” instead. A vault is never overwritten." = "「%@」已存在——已改为创建「%@」。保险库绝不会被覆盖。";

/* --- Settings / About / auto-lock --- */
"Auto-lock after inactivity:" = "不活动后自动锁定：";
"1 minute" = "1 分钟";
"5 minutes" = "5 分钟";
"15 minutes" = "15 分钟";
"30 minutes" = "30 分钟";
"Never" = "从不";
"The vault always locks on system sleep and screen lock. Inactivity is measured system-wide." = "在系统睡眠和锁屏时，保险库始终会锁定。不活动按整个系统范围计量。";
"About Farewell" = "关于 Farewell";
"sleep" = "睡眠";
"screen lock" = "锁屏";
"inactivity" = "不活动";
"Vault locked automatically (%@). Unlock to continue." = "保险库已自动锁定（%@）。请解锁以继续。";

/* --- Import failure reasons --- */
"vault not open" = "保险库未打开";
"empty name" = "名称为空";
"cannot stat %@" = "无法获取 %@ 的状态";
"cannot read %@" = "无法读取 %@";
"“%@” is %@ but only %@ is free in this level." = "「%@」为 %@，但此层级仅有 %@ 可用。";
"Not enough space: the edit needs %@ but only %@ is available." = "空间不足：此次编辑需要 %@，但仅有 %@ 可用。";

