"Clear search" = "清除搜索";
"Rename…" = "重命名…";
"Rename folder…" = "重命名文件夹…";
"New subfolder…" = "新建子文件夹…";
"Move to top level" = "移动到顶层";
"Delete folder" = "删除文件夹";
"Passes" = "遍数";
"Select a file to view it." = "选择一个文件以查看。";
"Cannot preview" = "无法预览";
"Failed to load" = "加载失败";
"Fullscreen (Esc to exit)" = "全屏（按 Esc 退出）";
"Copy this Mac’s serial number" = "复制此 Mac 的序列号";

/* --- Clé matérielle initiale + clarté clé de secours (ajout) --- */
"Adding a backup happens in two steps — and the order matters:" = "添加备份密钥分两步——顺序很重要：";
"**1.** First insert your **current key** (the one that already opens this vault) and touch it — **not the new key yet**." = "**1.** 先插入你的**当前密钥**（已经能打开此保险库的那个）并轻触它——**先别碰新密钥**。";
"**2.** Only then, when asked, swap to the **new backup key** and touch it twice." = "**2.** 然后在提示时，再换成**新的备份密钥**并轻触两次。";
"Either key will then open the vault. Keep the backup somewhere safe and separate — there's no recovery if you lose every key." = "之后任一密钥都能打开此保险库。请将备份密钥保存在安全且独立的地方——若丢失所有密钥，将无法恢复。";
"Enter your passphrase to add a hardware key." = "输入你的密码短语以添加硬件密钥。";
"Adding your hardware key…" = "正在添加你的硬件密钥…";
"Enrolling your hardware key…" = "正在注册你的硬件密钥…";
"Hardware key enrolled. This vault now needs that key plus your passphrase to open. Enrol a backup key too — lose your only key and the vault is gone, with no recovery." = "硬件密钥已注册。现在打开此保险库需要该密钥加上你的密码短语。也请注册一个备份密钥——若丢失唯一的密钥，保险库将丢失且无法恢复。";
"Hardware key enrolled. Unlock again to continue." = "硬件密钥已注册。请重新解锁以继续。";
"Could not add the hardware key: %@. Your vault is unchanged." = "无法添加硬件密钥：%@。你的保险库未更改。";
"Touch your new key now" = "现在轻触你的新密钥";
